OL,3,CParents whose son died in off-road
OL,4,Cbike crash channel grief into giving
OL,5,Cback
OL,7,FNicola and Steven Wright, from
OL,8,FMiddlesbrough, began fundraising for
OL,9,Fthe Great North Air Ambulance Service
OL,10,Ffollowing the death of their son Mason
OL,11,Fin 2021.
OL,13,FThe couple are among those nominated
OL,14,Fas finalists for the ITV News Tyne
OL,15,FTees Pride of Britain Regional
OL,16,FFundraiser of the Year award.
OL,18,FEach year four people or teams are
OL,19,Fchosen for their incredible work
OL,20,Fraising money for charity.
