OL,3,CParents whose son died in off-road
OL,4,Cbike crash channel grief into giving
OL,5,Cback
OL,7,FMason was treated at the scene of his
OL,8,Faccident by the Great North Air
OL,9,FAmbulance, and was airlifted to James
OL,10,FCook University Hospital - but he did
OL,11,Fnot survive.
OL,13,FJust months after his death, Nicola
OL,14,Fand Steven began tirelessly raising
OL,15,Fmoney to give back to the charity that
OL,16,Fhelped them on their darkest day.
OL,18,FTheir fundraising efforts in Mason's
OL,19,Fname is hoped to continue to help keep
OL,20,Fhis memory alive.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/7
