OL,3,CParents whose son died in off-road
OL,4,Cbike crash channel grief into giving
OL,5,Cback
OL,7,FNicola said: "It keeps me going and
OL,8,Fkeeps me right, so that's why I do it.
OL,9,FAnd if I didn't do this, Mason
OL,10,Fwouldn't be spoken about on a daily
OL,11,Fbasis. So that's why I do it, with the
OL,12,Fhelp of my community."
OL,14,FThe couple have held sponsored walks
OL,15,Fcalled 'Miles for Mason', bike rides,
OL,16,Fa sky dive, participated in Sober
OL,17,FOctober and held family fun days.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/7
