OL,5,Cback
OL,7,FThe list goes, while the couple say it
OL,8,Fis thanks to the support of their
OL,9,Fcommunity in Middlesbrough that has
OL,10,Fenabled them to reach the #37,000 mark.
OL,12,FEvery penny goes back to the Great
OL,13,FNorth Air Ambulance, a charity that
OL,14,Fprovides life saving, critical care in
OL,15,Femergency situations.
OL,17,FBen Sisson, from the charity, told ITV
OL,18,FTyne Tees: "The difference that that
OL,19,Fkind of money makes is so so valuable."
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G5/7
