OL,7,FHe added: "That can operate the base
OL,8,Ffor a couple of days, or that's six or
OL,9,Fseven life saving missions, as it's
OL,10,Falmost #5,000 per mission, giving
OL,11,Fpeople the very very best chance on
OL,12,Ftheir worst day.
OL,14,F"They are ultimately saving lives and
OL,15,Fleaving a legacy that will last a long
OL,16,Flong time."
